will see good performance of its economy in 1998.
</P>
<P>
"We should have a very good year in 1998, not for all the
people because there are jobless people in very difficult
situation, but globally, the French economy will have a good year
in 1998," said Strauss-Kahn in an interview with TF1 television
station Sunday evening.
</P>
