term ends. His supporters last year tried in vain to amend the
Constitution to extend his term of office.
</P>
<P>
The power failure caused by a technical problem resulted in a
blackout on the Luzon island, one of the three main islands of the
Philippines. It took the technicians almost 12 hours to restore
power supply to Metro Manila. 
