Kuwaiti national, arrived in Iran in 1991 through Iran's southern
port city of Bandar Abbas and took charge of espionage in
Khorramshahr and Ahvaz, capital of the Khuzestan province.
</P>
<P>
The daily added that Sultan is in custody, but the others, who
are Iranians, have been freed on bail.
</P>
<P>
The Iranian political or legal authorities have so far not
confirmed the arrests. 
