<HEADLINE> Vietnam's Party Leader Vows to Stick to Socialism </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, January 5 (Xinhua) -- New General Secretary of the
Communist Party of Vietnam Le Kha Phieu vowed that Vietnam
is determined to stick to socialism and renovation.
</P>
