accomplish the 11-point socio-economic program included in the
resolution of the eighth party congress."
</P>
<P>
Referring to foreign relations, Le said, "we will continue
with our foreign policy of independence, respect of sovereignty,
peace, friendship and multilateralization of relations, and to be
friends with all countries."
</P>
<P>
He stressed that "developing economy is the central task,
building the party is the key and maintaining political stability
is the fundamental condition to carry out the renewal process."
